{"tid":2448854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會唔會將資金分散落唔同既投資 定 all in 落股票","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T22:26:06.000Z","uid":167915,"like":13,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0dcae61a5be6f1ee555793bdc8d539d70b523c","tid":2448854,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"小弟大概2020年開始接觸投資<br />\n一開始跟朋友中銀玩月供+港股<br />\n銀行正係買入費都要50蚊一次 又要收存倉費 <br />\n港股手續費又貴<br />\n去到3月洩錢多過賺<br />\n到8月咁常下 開左牛牛户口 發覺手續費便啲<br />\n轉做正係玩港股 妹下妹下 閒閒地都坐成個月先賺少少<br />\n<br />\n大概8月到就開始玩基金 發現都有穩定性增長<br />\n到今年1月到就玩埋美股 一個月既profit 係2020年既幾倍<br />\n所以依家投資策略就一半基金 一半美股<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁常下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAll in <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cd1fcdb3db7388f71f3051e981acdea37cfba6","tid":2448854,"uid":134774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"what基金"},{"pid":"54f048de1c25457d2dd89f90580aa6aca6ae79be","tid":2448854,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"出呢個post亦當係俾自己既投資路做一個record"},{"pid":"7bdc6fb597b741bdbda15955d2ef55b2bb342da7","tid":2448854,"uid":167915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31cd1fcdb3db7388f71f3051e981acdea37cfba6","tid":2448854,"uid":134774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"what基金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"唔同基金都有 我自己諗法同供mpf 類似 但就有得自己控制幾時出入"},{"pid":"33e5016298fe30716483566f79ac77cf612472b5","tid":2448854,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"集中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要真正了解個間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ec62e2bca1f0346cc41c6f9b7bd588e0d37999","tid":2448854